733d899aacf1e96f90220be01","tid":1968193,"uid":66236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"娘親之前係蘋果見到尼份報道，佢覺得勁感動，<br />\n就帶我去食下尼間黃店<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/food/20200311/ICRCMPWBEKB3FVXIKD7SKUDUUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffood%2F20200311%2FICRCMPWBEKB3FVXIKD7SKUDUUY%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=c5b43e2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffood%2F20200311%2FICRCMPWBEKB3FVXIKD7SKUDUUY%2F&h=5fbed6aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/food/20200311/ICRCMPWBEKB3FVXIKD7SKUDUUY/</a><br />\n<br />\n推介原因：<br />\n1）抵食兼大份<br />\n雙餸飯係$28！加$7就已經有大大碗無味精嘅湯<br />\n尼個完全係大學canteen價，啲餸唔係得少少，而真係滿左個飯盒！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CqqggNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCqqggNJ.jpg&h=5432946a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n+$12 有份新鮮水果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yyFW1gq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyyFW1gq.png&h=0069c87d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算係扒餐，burger都係$60-70，係飽肚兼合理價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RPdYu9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRPdYu9m.jpg&h=6beab570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）有人情味<br />\n- 佢地keep住有俾啲飯盒（free/低價）俾學生同老人家<br />\n<br />\n- 今日等緊外賣嘅時候，聽到以下對話<br />\n兩個女人：之後要少啲出街，開始唔夠口罩<br />\n一個街友（餐廳受惠者）：我不嬲有帶多幾個口罩係身，俾幾個你呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感覺尼到係建立緊一個社會，受助嘅人同時係到助人，好有愛呀<br />\n<br />\n3）有質素食物<br />\n老老豆豆，講黃，佢一定唔係黃到金個啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/11/204205_19ecdb2dce953b0bd74a9069f35d11ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F11%2F204205_19ecdb2dce953b0bd74a9069f35d11ad.png&h=e8729963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而今日見到佢晚市，極少人，唔知佢可以頂到幾耐，<br />\n但食物真係有質素！純粹覺得有質素嘅餐廳值得俾更多人認識！<br />\n<br />\n今日食左尼個香草檸檬雞扒，塊扒大過我塊面，無骨，嫩滑，牛油果新鮮夠香，沙津菜唔苦，$65 真心覺得抵食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZATi2Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZATi2Q.png&h=25fea9f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TDVLUBj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTDVLUBj.png&h=8ad6ad47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話我打手都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望多啲人去幫襯<br />\n#黃色經濟圈 #好人一世平安"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:23:18.000Z","msg":"就咁睇一定好食過龍門好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f2250cd6f08d6d326ad067f17b6fbcd4283d73","tid":1968193,"uid":255313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4050c39e64ceec4597471966655a28bc946ebfd0","tid":1968193,"uid":82895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T16:27:50.000Z","msg":"係咪真黃 係就貨金支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T19:28:50.000Z","msg":"老闆/員工係黃，會一齊屌柒婆嗰隻(當然唔會爆粗)<br />\n612休半市<br />\n10月4晚開通宵比手足休息<br />\n有幾期突破breakazine講抗爭 有擺出嚟比人睇"},{"pid":"8afe303a567ecf805b05f171024ce6b09b465788","tid":1968193,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T20:27:02.000Z","msg":"請支持黃店<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200503/NSUFIPDRQTLOUCKYNIWBAS3QJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200503%2FNSUFIPDRQTLOUCKYNIWBAS3QJE%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=25592283\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200503%2FNSUFIPDRQTLOUCKYNIWBAS3QJE%2F&h=b3ceb056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200503/NSUFIPDRQTLOUCKYNIWBAS3QJE/</a>"},{"pid":"c420aafac5774c19bba4e8f4f12d719e8504e986","tid":1968193,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"